Class AbstractProjection<Event,​Effect>

  • java.lang.Object
    • gov.nasa.jpl.aerie.merlin.timeline.effects.AbstractProjection<Event,​Effect>
  • Type Parameters:
    Event - The type of event to be mapped into effects.
    Effect - The type of effect that will be combined according to the event graph structure.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    EffectTrait<Effect>, Projection<Event,​Effect>
    public abstract class AbstractProjection<Event,​Effect>
extends Object
implements Projection<Event,​Effect>
    An abstract class implementing EffectTrait by delegation.

    Only the abstract method Projection.atom(Event) needs to be implemented by a subclass. The remaining abstract methods of the Projection class will be delegated to an EffectTrait provided at time of construction.
